==== 相簿 ====
[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#相簿]] 可以儲存自訂照片. 自訂照片可用於多種用途, 例如做為用戶個人檔案的備用頭像. 照片也可以在邀請其他用戶時使用. 照片也可以用在群組的橫幅, 並加入群組相簿內.

==== 拍立得 ====
[[Special:MyLanguage/Prints|拍立得]] 是用戶在 VRChat 中拍攝的照片, 這些照片可以作為物體在世界中生成, 供其他用戶分享與保存. 若照片是在公共世界中拍攝, 且已在相機設置中啟用相關功能，拍立得將包含元數據, 包括拍攝者、拍攝地點以及拍攝時間. 其外觀與現實世界中的 [[Wikipedia:Instant_film|拍立得相紙]] 相同。

用戶可通過將拍立得保存至他的 [[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory|物品欄]] 中來"收集"這些拍立得。

==== 頭像 ====
[[File:VRChat Plus Icons.webp|thumb|200x200px|VRC+ 訂閱者的頭像可以顯示在名牌上.]]
[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#User Icons|頭像]] 是圓形圖像, 可用於個人資料及群組. 裝備後, 該頭像將顯示在用戶的名牌上、快捷菜單頂部的「此處」選項卡中以及個人資料頁上, 並會替換由用戶名前三個字構成的默認頭像.

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==== Custom emoji ====
<!-- make sound beter plox -->
Up to nine custom [[Special:MyLanguage/Emojis#Custom stickers|emoji]] can be uploaded and used in the Inventory, providing unique expressions and reactions. Animated emoji are also supported.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==== Custom stickers ====
Custom [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers#Custom stickers|stickers]] can be uploaded similarly to how custom emojis are. Stickers are placeable images that any user can see, only one can be placed at a time. When a user leaves an instance, their stickers will disappear. Users can hide a sticker by selecting it, blocking a user will also hide their stickers.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==== UI decorations ====
Supporters can customize UI elements to their liking, including the UI theme colors and selecting background designs for the [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu|Quick Menu]] and [[Special:MyLanguage/Main Menu|Main Menu]].
</div>

